<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Relieving and Experience Letter</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Cambria', serif;
      font-size: 12pt;
      color: #000;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 35mm 25mm 25mm 25mm; /* Balanced margins like your right-side original */
      line-height: 1.6;
      position: relative;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .date {
      text-align: right;
      margin: 0 0 15pt 0;
    }

    .title {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: underline;
      margin: 0 0 20pt 0;
    }

    .paragraph {
      margin: 0 0 14pt 0;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .sincere-line {
      margin-top: 28pt;
      margin-bottom: 3pt;
    }

    .for-company-line {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 8pt;
    }

    .signature-block {
      margin-top: 4pt;
    }

    .signature-block img {
      width: 80px;
      height: auto;
      opacity: 0.95;
      display: block;
      margin: -8px 0 5px 8px;
    }

    .hr-details {
      margin-top: 2pt;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 10pt;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20mm;
      left: 25mm;
      right: 25mm;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <p class="date"><%= relieving_date %></p>
    <p class="title">Relieving and Experience Letter</p>

    <p class="paragraph">Employee Name: <%= employee_name %></p>
    <% if (employee_id) { %>
      <p class="paragraph">Employee ID: <%= employee_id %></p>
    <% } %>

    <p class="paragraph">
      This is with regard to your resignation, dated
      <%= resignation_date %> from the position of
      <strong><%= designation %></strong>. We would like to inform you that you have been relieved of your duties at the end of business hours of <%= relieving_date %>.
    </p>

    <p class="paragraph">
      We enjoyed working with you and thank you for the service rendered from
      <strong><%= start_date %></strong> to
      <strong><%= relieving_date %></strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="paragraph">We wish you good luck for future endeavours.</p>

    <p class="sincere-line">Yours sincerely,</p>
    <p class="for-company-line">For Amazon IT Solutions</p>

    <div class="signature-block">
      <% if (signaturePath) { %>
        <img src="<%= signaturePath %>" alt="Authorized Signature" />
      <% } %>

      <div class="hr-details">
        <p><strong><%= hrName %></strong></p>
        <p><%= hrDesignation %></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="note">Note: This is a computer-generated document. No Signature is required*</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
